  "author": "Matthew Pogue",
  "description": "Dark theme inspired by the olivia++ keycaps. To alter theme, find it hosted at github.com/poguepotamus/firefox_themes. This may also be of some use. https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/theme",
